# Tour Management System

A full-stack Tour Management System developed using Java, JSP, Servlets, JDBC, PostgreSQL, HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

## Features

- User Registration & Login
- Forgot Password
- Browse Tours
- Search Tours
- Tour Booking
- My Bookings
- Cancel Booking
- Responsive UI
- PostgreSQL Database

## Technologies Used

- Java
- JSP & Servlets
- JDBC
- PostgreSQL
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript
- Maven
- Apache Tomcat

## Project Structure

- MVC Architecture
- DAO Pattern
- Session Management
- Database Connectivity

## Future Improvements

- Payment Gateway
- Email Notifications
- Admin Dashboard
- Online Deployment

